867
01:02:40,890 --> 01:02:43,550
<i>Let's save him first.</i>

868
01:02:43,630 --> 01:02:46,430
<i>Nothing works out because of you!</i>

869
01:02:46,430 --> 01:02:48,050
<i>You fox!</i>

870
01:02:49,740 --> 01:02:51,220
<i>Who are you?</i>

871
